          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Elder Poverty Relief Act</b></p> <p>This bill&nbsp;establishes a new poverty-relief benefit under the Old Age, Survivors, and Disability Insurance (OASDI) program for certain individuals entitled to OASDI benefits, disability insurance benefits, or benefits under the Supplemental Security Income program.</p>]]></text>
